SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT cast (sum (LGCC_AMOUNTC) as decimal (18,2)), cast (sum (LGCC_AMOUNTH) as decimal (18,2)) FROM :1/LGCC WHERE LGCC_LGCD_ADMNO= :2 and :3 and LGCC_DATE :4 and LGCC_ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO = :5 and LGCC_ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO = :6 FOR FETCH ONLY OPTIMIZE FOR 100 ROWS

select inud_datefrom,inud_dateuntil,inud_interestamountc from :1/inud,:1/invo where invo_admno=:2 and invo_clntno=:3 and inud_invo_no = invo_no and :4 and ( INUD_BOOKINGTYPE=1 or INUD_BOOKINGTYPE=2 ) FOR FETCH ONLY OPTIMIZE FOR 100 ROWS
